The breath is short...I'm alone in the winter. 
Do you want it? Do you want this existance...its more than crimson paint and raven silk..it's here, inside me all of the time. This tune which the toneless melody rings true. It's hell within the confines of the exterior of harsh bone and flushed skin.  
	The tears of my flesh meld with the honey bleakness of the snow. I can feel it course through me...but am I saved? Am I yet next to you? The one true and desperate love of my life? Your name is felicidade and you live on the island before me. Forever lost and against the hollow trees. I'll hide away. That ace in front of the long whales of blue tears...it cheats its way into life. She's like the river towards the lightning. I must have done something wrong...when I ask who am I...I don't have an answer. And isn't that usual? Sleep is my enemy, I hate the esence of helplesness...like I need any help in such a situation. I am helpless and fragile. I am lost...at a loss for my own way in the world. I am small...my lips are frozen in a terrified kiss because dancing with death is not the light of the hollowed bark. Crushing souls...my defenses deeply within their troubled slumber. And I curse it..I curse the son of a bitch who lit the black-flamed candle. What is to be done about her tortured soul? What can we do to stop her rediculous tears? The wanton acts of desire in which we stand with, hand in hand. Love you honey...love you more than anything in the world. Though the earth is dirt in a glass shpere. I loved you from the moment I say the crystal in your eyes. From the moment your innocent meldoy rang out in the middle of the night. I was there..and now you hate me...now you despise everything that I am. The life I gave you was undoubtfully mine. I shared with you the objects of my spirit. I gave you a part of my soul...and you despise me. I have slept, burried deep within the white blankets. The stone above me, the wood around me, the confides of my sleep closing in about me. I hated that place. The howling above me. Now I feel cold. Somebody help me.

This was a poem I wrote yesterday on the bus in a faded black pen (cause pens are so damned unreliable!) I wrote it at the start of the story of my life. A life story....I'm losing more sleep now and it gets harder and harder to get up every morning. I reckon in the space of a week I've only had 10hrs sleep. Is it insomnia? Or is it just my sickening fear which I feel? Either way, I know it has to stop. I have to go and see a councellor. I know I keep saying this and never do it...but there's nothing else I can do. I've never felt so alone. And that's a horrible feeling when you're surrounded by people who love you. Because nobody understands and it shits me to tears. I don't expect anyone to understand but it gets so hard to be alone. To know that there are other people there...but they're not really there. I hate that feeling. Like I said, it has to stop. I've lost the second story card but I'll look them up in the phone book and call to make an appointment. I have my family, and they don't want to listen...I have my friends and they just...don't know what to say. Why do I even bother sometimes...I just have no idea. If there's nothing keeping me going then why am I still here? Because I am loved I can't deny that. I won't say that there is noone who cares about me because that would be a lie. I don't want to lie anymore. I don't want to say that I'm happy when I'm not...you know. I don't really fit in anywhere. I'm not in any category, that makes me so fuckin depressed. Even people who are depressed have a place. I have no place. I don't fit in anywhere. To walk towards the glass My white limbs are still trembling Again I had to ask The flames about me embering The hate in which I feel Flows straight into my heart The skies grown hard of steel My melodies of art The chill upon my flesh Never can compare To death my soul would mesh and the lonliness I found there The sun would never rise The night would show its teeth Until my sweet demise My blood will go unsheathed
I am tired (an insomniac) I hate sleep more than waking but still...I'm getting sick from it.

1. what do you plan on doing with your life, like what would you like to become ? There are a couple of things that I would like to do really when I grow up. I would really love to have a family (but that's not the first thing I want to do) I want to study english at university along with drama, photography and anthrapology. Although I'm not exactly sure as to what I want to do, I would love to be a stage actress. Perhaps waitressing to back me up? But I'm not exactly sure yet. Those are just a few options. 2. what's your favourite animal and why ? I have to confess that my favourite animal is the wolf. They keep together in packs and work as a team to acheive their goals. It reminds me of the kind of society that humans should co-exist in. working together without conflict, protecting and caring for each other. These magestic animals also seem to posses a certain charm about them that is just unquestionable. 3. you have a liking for music, what's your top ten of all time songs ? Hmmm...my top ten huh? er... I'll put them in a list (they're not in order, I like them all the same) v "Bleed for me" featured in the daredevil album performed by saliva v "beautiful day" by U2- (the song has a flowing energy that I absolutely love) v "crawling" by Linkin park hybrid theory v "hand me down" matchbox20 more than you think you are v "downfall" matchbox20 more than you think you are v "real world" matchbox20 (I don't remember :S) v "my immortal" evanesence fallen v "elevation" U2 v With or without you U2 the joshua tree v Iris-goo goo dolls 4. you believe in other life in another univerise ? I believe that we can't be so narrow minded as to think that there is no other life out there in a space so enormous. There must be life in another universe somewhere. We can't be alone. 5. what's the colour witch you love ? I love the colour purple. I guess it's just an immitation of my mother because I idolize my mum. I love her strangth and her wisdom. Her favourite colour is purple and I decided that was mine too a long time ago and so the feeling stuck.

I have been thinkin a few many thoughts...I want to meet some of my fellow adelaidian Lj friends. 

All my friends who live in Adelaide I reckon we should meet up in town or something. 

comment and tell me what you think

~Alex

I am The Empress

The Empress can refer to any aspect of Motherhood. She can be an individual mother, but as a major arcana card, she also goes beyond the specifics of mothering to its essence - the creation of life and its sustenance through loving care and attention. The Empress can also represent lavish abundance of all kinds. She offers a cornucopia of delights, especially those of the senses - food, pleasure and beauty. She can suggest material reward, but only with the understanding that riches go with a generous and open spirit. The Empress asks you to embrace the principle of life and enjoy its bountiful goodness.

For a full description of your card and other goodies, please visit LearnTarot.com

There are few times in my life (that I remember) when I've known anything for sure. Now I know stuff for sure.

It's a really strange feeling you know? I've just suddenly realized alot of things about myself and I don't know why. I am really interested in the ancient ways of the world. Like ancient Egypt, or Japan or China, Greece, Rome. Everything. It's a strange feeling. 

I also decided that I want to study Anthropology at university along with English, Drama and Photography. 

My friend just had a baby and I realized (well, something I've always known...) That I want a family when I grow up too. I want to have kids and a nice house and a nice husband. (Anyone want to volunteer to give me this life;))

It's a strange feeling like I've said. I don't want to be just another one of those teenagers who write poetry and short stories in their early years but never move to do anything about becoming an author. I really, desperatly want to be an author when I grow up later on.

I've always wanted to be an Author. Always, I hope that in the future that dream will become a reality.

There are some things that fall and some things that stand
Some things that I can't feel anymore and some things I don't want to feel.
Can you really tell me that I am wrong? 
But around the fire flutters to the ground ever so softly like the cinders after the eruption. 
That is how I feel when I wake, that feeling I don't want

The drowziness of everyday blabber along the courts of shattered stone. 

That shattered stone may as well be my soul frozen on the ground. My lips turned to nothing less than the sucked lust and less of my heart...

chapter one; 
things i need to learn

the soapy water slushed around my hands as i scraped the rest of last night's pasta off of the dinner plate.
i think it's weird the way night-time works, there are moths scattered along the surface of the kitchen window seeking the light from inside, why are they Nocternal if they don't like the darkness? i think they remind me of myself, wanting something i obviously wasn't meant to have. 
it has been 8 years since then and the nightmares haven't faded from my already troubled mind, it is like a torture to close my eyes, but it's even harder to open them in the morning. 
by the time day breaks i'd have already been awake for at least 4 hours covered in a cold sweat, alone, tired and frightened. there is nobody to share this pain with, nobady who knows they need to care. 
people don't seem to understand why i cry at night, when i remain silent when they ask me how i am that morning. even if i told them why they still wouldn't understand. 
it's like living in hell, only everything looks and feels exactly the same as it did the day before when you stepped out your front door.
sometimes i feel as though i'm stranded on a desert island with no-one to talk to and no-one to love...


tell me what you think yeah?

thanks

-alex

........................................................................................i thought i should start by doing that...dunno why. 

i got a day off yesterday and saw American pie wedding. my parents got pissed coz i didn't do my room before i left (how childish does that sound...?)

so yeah, i got over that. but lately i've felt really lonely among my family and everything.

well last night it started when i said there was something wrong with me (i'd rather not go into what it was, medical shit, y'know?)
anyway, so my parents can't see what's wrong with me, and they think i'm fuckin' stupid for wasting my time trying to tell them about it. 

i was intent on nothing, my sister was like "don't worry about it." and i said, "you would worry." that's not even the point, if my younger brother/mummy's boy had something wrong with him, they would be worried, they wouldn't tell him to fuck off like they do to me.
i went for a walk to the close-by delih at 7:30, it was dark and my sister came with me. i had the full "i mean business" stride going on. 
it's like everything i do is wrong now. 
see, my sister started drinking and going out with boys, smoking and shit when she was my age so they're being hard on me for it. 
my mum says, "you're getting more like casey every day." that's pretty bad, (no offence to my sis) but my parents fuckin' hate her. so i went from invisible to bloody hated. 

then my mum says "what's wrong. you're nearly crying. you're never happy."

i said "maybe i should work on being a better daughter then. y'know whenever i tell you what's wrong you call me stupid. i feel like nothing around you." 
"when did i say anything like that?" 
"when i told you about the dream i had (you read it in an earlier post) you said it's just a dream." 
"what? i can't change your dreams alex" 
"i wasn't asking you to, you weren't even sympathetic. how the hell would you like to be raped and then have a reacuring dream about it haunting you for five years every night? and then have no-one understand how you feel, so they just tell you to stop being stupid."
i was out of breath after saying that. my mum turned off the light and told me to leave.
after that i locked myself in the bathroom and cried for about an hour. 

but my mascara didn't even run, i have to buy that more often.

i'm going to get councelling on the 29th with "shane"

i'm really really depressed now..........
